#: ../../index.rst:6 a5e734e08e4642a0936a2c68952bc16e
msgid ""
"`SafePassage <https://github.com/search5/safe-passage>`_ is a secure, "
"lightweight `Obsidian <https://obsidian.md>`_ plugin that links your "
"local KeePass databases (``.kdbx``) to your vault, rendering masked "
"credential chips and structured tables directly inside your notes — "
"without ever storing your master passwords or secrets in plain text."
msgstr ""
"`SafePassage <https://github.com/search5/safe-passage>`_ 는 로컬 KeePass "
"데이터베이스(``.kdbx``)를 볼트에 연결하여, 마스터 암호나 비밀 정보를 평문으"
"로 저장하지 않으면서 노트 안에 마스킹된 자격 증명 칩과 구조화된 표를 직접 "
"렌더링해 주는 안전하고 가벼운 `Obsidian <https://obsidian.md>`_ 플러그인입"
"니다."
